topic.title: Wound Measurement Observation - conformance rules

section.p: This template represents the Wound Measurement Observations of wound width, depth and length.

ol.li:
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] templateId ( CONF:1098-29928, CONF:1098-29929 ) such that it
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @root="2.16.840.1.113883.10.20.22.4.133"
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @classCode="OBS" Observation (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.5.6 HL7ActClass) (CONF:1098-29926)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] @moodCode="EVN" Event (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.5.1001 HL7ActMood) (CONF:1098-29927)
SHALL contain at least one [1..*] id (CONF:1098-29930)
SHALL contain exactly one [1..1] code, which SHALL be selected from ValueSet Wound Measurements 2.16.840.1.113883.1.11.20.2.5 DYNAMIC (CONF:1098-29931)
